All symbols pay from the leftmost reel to the right on active paylines when landing consecutively and meeting the required number of matches.
All values are expressed as actual coin wins.
Only the highest win is paid per payline.
Wins on multiple paylines are added together.

Win = A  B
A: Odds
B: Total Bet

Wild appears on all reels during the FREE SPINS round.
Substitutes for all symbols except SCATTER.
SCATTER symbols can appear on all reels during the base game.

At every spin the MONEY symbol takes a random value, possible values are 2x, 5x, 10x, 15x, 20x, 25x, 50x, 2000x total bet.
The fish paying symbols are also MONEY symbols. At every spin, the fish take a random money value which can be won during the FREE SPINS bonus game.

Any 3, 4, 5 Scatter symbols appearing anywhere on the screen trigger 10, 15, 20 FREE SPINS feature respectively. 
3 Scatters  awards 10 Free Spins
4 Scatters  awards 15 Free Spins
5 Scatters  awards 20 Free Spins

Bonus game are treated as same round with the spin which trigger it. The total bet and max win will continue during bonus game.
Special reels are in play during the feature.

Every 4th WILD symbol collected, retriggers the bonus game, awards 10 more free spins and the multiplier for MONEY symbol collection increases to 2x for the first retrigger, 4x for the second retrigger.
The retriggered spins are played after the previous batch of free spins ends.
The multiplier applies to the retriggered spins.
After the second retrigger, the feature cannot be retriggered anymore.

Randomly, when there is only 1 WILD symbol without any fish MONEY Symbol on the screen, at the end of that free spin, a boot will be fish and 1 more free spin will be add to that batch.
Max 3 more free spins may be added during that round.

FREE SPINS = 50x Total Bet
Instantly receive 3+ Scatter symbols and trigger the corresponding number of free spins upon purchase.

1. Prizes shown in points/currency. 

2. During or after free games, if no screen tap occurs within 10 seconds, the game continues automatically.

3. If a malfunction allows the game to continue, the system completes it and ensures you receive earned winnings.

4. During the game, if there is any malfunction or disconnection, the final betting records will base on system's database. 

5. Our company reserve the right to adjudicate and provide the final interpretation of all bets.

1. Click on the Spin button to start a game.
2. Pressing the spacebar once can also start a game.
3. Click on the Auto button to play the game automatically.
Click +/- to increase/decrease the bet amount.
Click to open the pop-up for auto spin settings.
Set the number of auto spins. Click the spin count menu to select other options.
When enabled, if a free game is triggered in the game, auto-spin will stop after the free game ends. When disabled, this feature will not be active.

The game has 3 speeds to choose from. If not activated, it will be at normal speed.
QUICK SPIN: 1x speed
TURBO SPIN: 2x speed
After clicking, the game will automatically spin according to the popup settings.
This button is located at the top right corner of the popup. After clicking, it cancels the popup settings and closes the popup.
Click to open all game menus. You can click the heart on the game to add it to your favorites list, and also click on the game to switch to another game.
(Click the button to cycle through the audio states.)
Audio is fully on, initially set to audio fully on.
Turn off all music and sound effects
Click once to maximize the game window; click once in the maximize screen to minimized the game window.(If available)
Click to open the history page.
Click to open the game instructions popup.
